# Project Overview Report

## Project Title
Implementation of Networking Topology and File Transfer Protocols

## Project Manager
Abhinandan  
pujariabhinandann@gmail.com  
Maalgudi Technolabs 

## Objective
The primary objective of this project is to implement a suitable networking topology that optimizes data flow and communication within a specific geographic area. Additionally, the project will facilitate secure file transfers using HTTPS and FTP protocols, ensuring reliable access and sharing of resources.
